	(text "0 Hz - 2 MHz (3rd Order, Shunt-First Butterworth filter)\nWe rely on the fact that AM radio transmissions are strong.\nWe may need to put a large capacitor at the beginning if DC\noffsets become an issue."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 120.396 96.52 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
